        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_Membership_ResetPassword",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to reset a user's password in an ASP.NET membership database. It handles the logic for updating the password, managing failed password attempts, and locking out users if necessary. The procedure ensures that the password reset process adheres to security policies, such as maximum invalid attempts and lockout mechanisms."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
